docs.lead_paragraph: Wrapup: This was a debate of several strong, sharp moments that may not have added up to a game-changer for Mrs. Clinton but it gave her a chance to get back to basics -- health care, fighter, woman -- and to express regret (again) for her vote for the war in Iraq.
